data.title: AFI’s 100 YEARS…100 HEROES & VILLAINS
data.meta_description: AFI's 100 Years...100 Heroes & Villains is a list of the 50 top movie heroes and 50 top movie villains of all time.The characters on this list have enriched America's film heritage while continuing to inspire contemporary artists and audiences.The AFI's 100 Years...100 Heroes & Villains television special, hosted by Arnold Schwarzenegger, who earned both a hero and villain honor for his portrayal of the
